statements.sql: select `users`.*, `customer_manager`.`manager_id` as `pivot_manager_id`, `customer_manager`.`customer_id` as `pivot_customer_id` from `users` inner join `customer_manager` on `users`.`id` = `customer_manager`.`customer_id` where `customer_manager`.`manager_id` = 1 and `role` = 1
select exists(select * from `users` inner join `customer_manager` on `users`.`id` = `customer_manager`.`manager_id` where `customer_manager`.`customer_id` = 3 and `role` = 2) as `exists`
select exists(select * from `users` inner join `customer_manager` on `users`.`id` = `customer_manager`.`manager_id` where `customer_manager`.`customer_id` = 4 and `role` = 2) as `exists`
